🏠 Demonstration of Proposed Features:

The House Analysis Dashboard developed using Tableau demonstrates the following key features:

->>Interactive Sales Overview
          Displays total sales, average house price, and yearly trends.
          Dynamic filters for year, region, and property type.
->>Regional Price Analysis
          Compares housing prices across different regions.
          Identifies high-demand and high-value locations.
->>Price Distribution Insights
          Visualizes price ranges using histograms and bar charts.
          Helps understand affordability patterns.
->>Trend Analysis
          Shows how housing prices change over time.
          Identifies growth patterns and seasonal variations.
->>User-Friendly Filters
          Allows users to select custom parameters.
          Real-time updates for better decision-making.
          The dashboard provides clear, interactive visual insights to help users analyze housing market trends effectively.
